name: Nightwalk - Takayama, Japan
description:
Backpacking Japan 1/10

I arrived to Takayama late in the afternoon after a long travel by train from Tokyo. After getting a bed in the local hostel I walked around the city. It was Tuesday or Wednesday, the city was almost empty and almost all business and restaurants were closed. A lonely old man was the only person I saw for about 1 hour.
